# E2E Flow Map — {project}

Source of truth for E2E coverage. **Before extending**: read the flow's entry,
reuse its action helpers, add the branch as a tagged test, flip ✅/⬜. **Before a
new flow**: add a section.

## Building blocks

| Concern | Location |
|---------|----------|
| Action helpers | `tests/e2e/actions/*` |
| Data + DB fixtures | `tests/e2e/fixtures/db.ts` |
| Auth / persisted session | `tests/e2e/global.setup.ts` → `tests/e2e/.auth/*.json` |

## Tag taxonomy

`@{flow}` (master) · `@create` · `@{outcome}` · `@{affordance}` · `@negative` ·
`@rbac` · `@critical`

## Selective runs

| Want | Command |
|------|---------|
| Master flow | `npx playwright test --grep @{flow} --project=chromium` |
| One branch | `npx playwright test --grep @{affordance} --project=chromium` |
| Exclude negatives | `npx playwright test --grep-invert @negative --project=chromium` |
| Watch slow | prefix `SLOWMO=800` + `--headed`, or `--ui` |

